Elective courses
If you have one major please choose 150 credits.

If you have one major and a minor choose 150 credits less the credit value of the minor(s). For example, if you have a 60 credit minor choose 90 elective credits, if you have a 75 credit minor choose 45 credits, if you have two 60 credit minors choose 30 elective credits.

If you have two majors please choose 15 elective credits.

Please contact us if you need help with your selections.
